OL,3,CSizewell C construction costs to add
OL,4,Cup to #19 to electricity bills, says
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FThe costs of building Sizewell C
OL,8,Fnuclear power station could cost
OL,9,Fhouseholds up to #19 a year on top of
OL,10,Ftheir electricity bills by the time it
OL,11,Fopens, according to the public
OL,12,Fspending watchdog.
OL,14,FLast year, the Government struck a
OL,15,Fdeal with investors to push ahead with
OL,16,Fthe power plant's construction, to the
OL,17,Fcost of around #38 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
