OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779246238
OL,3,CSizewell C construction costs to add
OL,4,Cup to #19 to electricity bills, says
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FConstruction on the project is
OL,8,Fexpected to be completed by summer
OL,9,F2039 and will power the equivalent of
OL,10,Fsix million UK homes for 60 years.
OL,12,FA report from the National Audit
OL,13,FOffice (NAO) published on Wednesday
OL,14,Fshowed that the cost of Sizewell C is
OL,15,Fexpected to increase electricity
OL,16,Fprices for the typical household by #4
OL,17,Fin 2025-26.
OL,19,FIt found that this would then rise as
OL,20,Fhigh as between #17 and #19 by the
OL,21,Ftime it opens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
