CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779246238
OL,3,CSizewell C construction costs to add
OL,4,Cup to #19 to electricity bills, says
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FThe NAO also highlighted the "novel
OL,8,Ffinance structure" used by the
OL,9,FDepartment for Energy Security and Net
OL,10,FZero (DESNZ) with support from
OL,11,Findustry investors who help support
OL,12,Fthe project.
OL,14,FThe Government is the biggest
OL,15,Fshareholder in the project with a
OL,16,F44.9% stake, but other investors
OL,17,Finclude Canadian investment fund La
OL,18,FCaisse with 20%, British Gas owner
OL,19,FCentrica with 15%, EDF with 12.5% and
OL,20,FAmber Infrastructure with an initial
OL,21,F7.6%.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
