OL,3,CSizewell C construction costs to add
OL,4,Cup to #19 to electricity bills, says
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FThe report said that financial returns
OL,8,Fto investors could cost consumers
OL,9,Fbetween #4 billion and #4.5 billion
OL,10,Funless they also help to reduce costs
OL,11,Fand the timeframe of the project.
OL,13,FBut it added that the project could
OL,14,Fprovide up to #18 billion of net
OL,15,Fbenefits for consumers, according to
OL,16,FGovernment modelling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
