CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779246238
OL,3,CSizewell C construction costs to add
OL,4,Cup to #19 to electricity bills, says
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FA DESNZ spokeswoman said: "Building
OL,8,Fnew nuclear is an investment this
OL,9,Fcountry must make, because it is the
OL,10,Fonly way to get our country off the
OL,11,Frollercoaster of volatile global gas
OL,12,Fmarkets.
OL,14,F"As the NAO confirms, this is a good
OL,15,Fdeal for consumers and taxpayers `
OL,16,Fleading to cheaper power for families,
OL,17,Fsaving #2 billion a year across the
OL,18,Fenergy system once built, and limiting
OL,19,Fthe impact on a typical household bill
OL,20,Fto an average of around #1 per month
OL,21,Fduring construction."
OL,26,@oD@[OUvD@AOU}D@UO]
