OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779246238
OL,3,CSizewell C construction costs to add
OL,4,Cup to #19 to electricity bills, says
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,8,F"Sizewell C forms a significant part
OL,9,Fof the Government's plan for a secure
OL,10,Fand affordable clean energy supply.
OL,12,F"There has been a concerted attempt to
OL,13,Flearn from the problems of previous
OL,14,Fnuclear power construction projects
OL,15,Fand other large infrastructure schemes.
OL,17,F"This has resulted in a novel
OL,18,Ffinancing structure and DESNZ will
OL,19,Fneed to monitor the risks to taxpayers
OL,20,Fand billpayers closely."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@XO]
